     <h2>Bartholom Wild to John Adams: A Translation</h2>
     
     <div class="docbody">
      <div class="opener">
       <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationLeft">Monsieur</td>
		<td class="salutationRight">Utrecht, 20 October 1780</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
      </div>
      <p>Your friend, Mr. Ceresier, asked me to send you some political pamphlets on current affairs, and here they are:</p>
